{"id": "1182376530341535854", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "刚打完第二章，怎么詹金死得这么快，没反应过来", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T17:42:12.327000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182378781948784761", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "关卡内的克味小文本补充作用ok，正文上帝视角气氛烘托到位，就剧情对话看起来有点不走心，第二章结尾往蜡像馆外面跑，就像编导说詹金必须死，就安排詹金一集就领盒饭😭😭既没有说情况怎么紧急詹金必须去，有没有说其他人想别的方法自救，主角一行就像看着她死一样", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T17:51:09.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182379439217193070", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "不过最后一关固定角色，越探索越靠近死亡，打不过全靠重生，只有一滴血，效果绝了", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T17:53:45.857000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182381528890744944", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一章看着也稀里糊涂，阅读能力下降（X）死了的女孩子是本来就感染了？然后救济院院长确实是好人，被医生坑了吗😵‍💫幽灵的安排是为了什么，找姐姐的一条支线吗", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T18:02:04.074000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182382321832304720", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "融蝕洪流要淹過主角一行人了，唯一的出口大門鑰匙只能靠詹金去拿。", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T18:05:13.126000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1181974764122804288"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1182378781948784761", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182396974171951116", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "呜呜我知道，感觉铺垫不够，情况的危险性，主角团对她的担忧，她粘上融蚀自我安慰的侥幸（这个写了），真的要死了应该有的恐惧遗憾而不是纯粹的勇敢和一往无前，都一笔带过了。姐姐接钥匙看她要死了一点情绪波动都没有，就死后扫墓。詹金活动的动力就是为了找姐姐，最后也没看出来她俩姐妹情深，刚认识一样，和新认识的主角团一个感情。白发看板娘看她要死了，说的话是没法救了，离她远点，一点想不起来詹金是为了救主角一行献身，纯理性判断利害判断，有点冷血。剧情里她死得轻飘飘的，扫墓和摄像头消沉一个月，又太刻意", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:03:26.516000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["589115953355423805"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1182382321832304720", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182396976671772672", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "关卡里打牌全是融蚀牌和不断的重生，这个没有出路的强撑绝望效果都比关卡外表现出来的好", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:03:27.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182396982300520478", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "剧情仔细看了，看得出来想下功夫，关卡里克苏鲁味（或者叫别的，我不知道）文字风格保持一致，有剧情隐喻+人设补充，这个很有特色了。主线上帝第三人称视角加对话，哪里死人有失踪主角去哪里调查，结尾再死一个的模板剧情。还没看第三章，觉得一二章有点可惜。", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:03:28.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "2️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182398958325219378", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "要我说，詹金拿钥匙，主角这边试图破坏门，找其他办法，顺便和姐姐聊天，说詹金以前的事，丰满人物形象，畅想下姐妹未来，立点flag，水点剧情。现在从赴死到死就一关，赶紧gameover赶紧杀青赶紧领盒饭赶紧第三章，其实对詹金的死还没啥实感", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:11:19.575000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182402401861382195", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "想到了，就一起说了，威廉学长被俘虏（？）被囚禁也积极自救，在干活，出其不意出场救主角，🤣🤣摄像头干嘛说人家咒真好看，明明刚刚气都不会喘了，危机感一下子没了，变喜剧了", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:25:00.578000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182402879370305596", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:26:54.425000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1182402879164780686", "filename": "SPOILER_IMG_1222.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 436064, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1182402879164780686/SPOILER_IMG_1222.png?ex=6a37923e&is=6a3640be&hm=9eecb8476ff6893c1831657928f9f29d09e31c889d749ae06d1666d75e6b6130&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182403790813544640", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "后面冷面但靠谱严谨认真很有安全感的学长追犯罪嫌疑人去了，对主角团说，别死了，突然变好兄弟捶肩膀说的话，本应该是能写得很苏的人设🥹", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:30:31.730000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182405088820592741", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "说代入感的话，有自命名失忆主角，又有第三人称旁白，这个上帝视角写的文字又不是摄像头看到的，感受到的。这样两个声音一起叙述，其实就变成读者跟着上帝视角看摄像头和角色巴拉巴拉了，摄像头的存在可有可无了。", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:35:41.199000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182406283723284540", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "摄像头又是失忆百年难遇链接别人强加金手指指挥官类型🤣🤣失忆人设没过去经历，玩家的确第一眼看起来容易代入。最好说主角过去的人都被存在性消灭还是啥所以都忘了所以失忆，要不失忆梗烂大街了", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:40:26.086000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1182408126079717387", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181974764122804288", "author_name": "xiexiedududu", "author_bot": false, "content": "以上个人看法，剧情还能更好，大家不同的看法都对（狗头狗头", "timestamp": "2023-12-07T19:47:45.338000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
